13:38.952 --> 13:40.253
- A LOT OF PEOPLE DO IT
FOR FREE, YOU KNOW.

13:40.287 --> 13:41.154
- YEAH, YEAH,
BUT YOU SAID

13:41.188 --> 13:43.490
