18:17.630 --> 18:20.600
- WORKING ON IT.

18:22.502 --> 18:23.436
- MORNING, SUNSHINE.

18:23.470 --> 18:26.606
[clears throat]
CAN I GET YOU ANYTHING ELSE?

18:26.639 --> 18:28.908
- UH, YEAH.
COME TO THINK OF IT.

18:28.941 --> 18:30.177
- MM.

18:30.210 --> 18:33.480
I'LL BE LATE FOR CLASS.

18:42.389 --> 18:43.456
- HEY.
[chuckles]

18:43.490 --> 18:47.327
DIDN'T YOUR MOTHER TEACH YOU
TO CROSS ON THE GREEN?

18:47.360 --> 18:48.528
- WHAT DID HE DO NOW?

18:48.561 --> 18:49.596
- NOTHING.

