HE WAS FUCKING.

18:56.536 --> 18:57.904
IT WAS SOME OTHER GUY.

18:57.937 --> 18:59.939
I COME HOME.
HE'S ON THE FUCKING COUCH.

18:59.972 --> 19:01.741
- ANOTHER HURRICANE
OFF THE COAST OF FLORIDA,

19:01.774 --> 19:04.411
ANOTHER EARTHQUAKE IN PERU.
SO WHAT ELSE IS NEW?

19:04.444 --> 19:06.913
- I-I GUESS I JUST THOUGHT
THAT NOW THAT WE'RE TOGETHER--

19:06.946 --> 19:09.882
- THINGS WOULD BE DIFFERENT.
BRIAN IS NEVER GONNA CHANGE.

19:09.916 --> 19:11.184
YOU KNOW THAT.

19:11.218 --> 19:13.386
- THEN WHY AM I THERE?

19:13.420 --> 19:16.389
- WELL, MAY--MAYBE BECAUSE YOU
GOT BASHED IN THE HEAD

19:16.423 --> 19:19.692
AND HE FEELS GUILTY.

19:19.726 --> 19:20.893
NO, I'M SORRY.

19:20.927 --> 19:22.329
I DIDN'T MEAN FOR IT
TO SOUND LIKE THAT.

19:22.362 --> 19:25.665
I--

19:25.698 --> 19:28.535
SORRY.

