19:38.478 --> 19:40.413
- STOP FRETTING, TEDDY.

19:40.447 --> 19:41.481
I HAVE A PLAN.

19:41.514 --> 19:43.750
- AT THIS POINT IN THE STORY,
I'M SO DESPERATE,

19:43.783 --> 19:45.918
I ACTUALLY STOP WHAT I'M DOING,
TURN TO YOU

19:45.952 --> 19:49.689
WITH A PLAINTIVE EXPRESSION,
AND ASK, "YOU DO?"

19:49.722 --> 19:51.591
- OF COURSE.

19:51.624 --> 19:54.527
AFTER YOU LOSE EVERYTHING
YOU HAVE IN THE WORLD,

19:54.561 --> 19:56.796
YOU MOVE IN
WITH MICHAEL AND ME.

19:56.829 --> 19:59.766
WE HAVE AN INFLATABLE MATTRESS
AND A SPARE KEY.

20:02.302 --> 20:03.603
- 10,000 DOWN THE DRAIN.

20:03.636 --> 20:05.738
11,000 DOWN THE DRAIN.

20:08.308 --> 20:09.442
- OKAY.

20:09.476 --> 20:10.743
I HAVE ANOTHER IDEA.

20:10.777 --> 20:12.812
- DOES IT INVOLVE BEGGING
AT AN OFF-RAMP

20:12.845 --> 20:14.781
OR SLEEPING
IN A CARDBOARD BOX?

20:14.814 --> 20:16.516
- NO. NO.

20:16.549 --> 20:20.720
ACTUALLY, IT INVOLVES...

20:20.753 --> 20:23.690
- ZACK O'TOOL.

20:23.723 --> 20:27.627
- REMEMBER HOW I TOLD YOU
YOU NEEDED SOMETHING BIGGER?

20:27.660 --> 20:30.630
