20:32.432 --> 20:35.468
EXCUSE ME, BOYS.
EXCUSE ME.

20:35.502 --> 20:37.637
AHEM, ZACK.
[chuckles]

20:37.670 --> 20:40.507
SO GOOD
TO SEE YOU AGAIN.

20:40.540 --> 20:43.743
- DID YOU REALLY EXPECT
A PORN STAR OF HIS MAGNITUDE

20:43.776 --> 20:44.877
TO REMEMBER YOU?

20:44.911 --> 20:47.514
- WELL, MAYBE
HE'LL REMEMBER THIS.

20:47.547 --> 20:49.982
[clears throat]

20:56.589 --> 20:58.958
- OH, YEAH, YOU WERE THE GUY
THAT WAS SUPPOSED TO BLOW ME.

20:58.991 --> 21:00.460
- RIGHT.

21:00.493 --> 21:01.761
- YEAH, AND I'M THE GUY
WHO PAID YOU TO DO IT.

21:01.794 --> 21:02.929
- YEAH.

21:02.962 --> 21:05.498
- SO WHAT, UH,
W-WHAT BRINGS YOU TO TOWN?

21:05.532 --> 21:08.401
- WORKING ON MY NEW FILM.

21:08.435 --> 21:10.637
IT'S A FOOTBALL EPIC.

21:10.670 --> 21:13.940
BACKSIDES IN MOTION.
CHECK IT OUT.

21:13.973 --> 21:16.976
- OH, UH, I-I LOVE ANYTHING
WITH SHOULDER PADS.

21:17.009 --> 21:18.645
[both laugh]
SO--

21:18.678 --> 21:20.647
- I GOTTA GO.

21:34.694 --> 21:37.964
- DIDN'T I TELL YOU
IT'S EVEN BIGGER IN PERSON?

21:37.997 --> 21:40.667
IT'S HUGE!

21:40.700 --> 21:43.470
- IT'S GARGANTUAN.

21:43.503 --> 21:45.772
- IT'S JUST WHAT YOU NEED.

21:45.805 --> 21:46.839
WHAT I NEED.

21:46.873 --> 21:48.841
[chuckles]
WHAT EVERYBODY NEEDS.

21:48.875 --> 21:50.977
COME ON.

21:53.880 --> 21:57.884
UH, SAY, ZACK...
- HEY, ZACK.

21:57.917 --> 21:59.452
- NOW WHAT?

21:59.486 --> 22:01.921
- WELL, MY--MY FRIEND
HAS THIS LIVE, UH, WEBSITE--

22:01.954 --> 22:03.089
- NOT INTERESTED.

22:03.122 --> 22:04.824
- UH, WELL,
SINCE YOU HAVE,

22:04.857 --> 22:06.959
YOU KNOW, A LEGION OF, UH,
OF FANS--

22:06.993 --> 22:08.995
- NOT INTERESTED.

22:09.028 --> 22:11.964
- WHAT BETTER WAY
TO PLUG YOUR NEW PICTURE?

22:11.998 --> 22:13.566
- [chuckles]

22:13.600 --> 22:16.569
