IS FOR AMATEURS, BOYS.

22:16.603 --> 22:19.372
- WE'LL GIVE YOU 1,000 BUCKS,
UH, A LIMOUSINE,

22:19.406 --> 22:22.809
UH, CHAMPAGNE,
AND YOUR OWN PERSONAL FLUFFER.

22:22.842 --> 22:24.444
- [whispers]
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

22:24.477 --> 22:25.745
