A FORTUNE!

22:25.778 --> 22:28.748
- WOULD YOU RATHER
LOSE ONE?

22:31.150 --> 22:35.455
- SO, ZACK, HOW ABOUT SHARING
YOUR MEMBER

22:35.488 --> 22:37.857
