22:41.027 --> 22:42.995
- SEXY, PERFECT BODY.

22:43.029 --> 22:45.998
ALOOF, DESIRABLE,
YET UNATTAINABLE.

22:46.032 --> 22:48.134
- OKAY, OKAY,
THAT'S ENOUGH ABOUT ME.

22:48.167 --> 22:50.470
- I WAS REFERRING
TO THE SILVER SURFER.

22:50.503 --> 22:51.971
THIS SPEECH IS FOR SHIT.

22:52.004 --> 22:53.706
- WELL, WHY'D YOU AGREE?

22:53.740 --> 22:55.608
- THE PROFESSOR'S
REALLY CUTE.

22:55.642 --> 22:57.777
- REALLY?

22:57.810 --> 22:58.945
- OH, YOU CAN PUT THAT IDEA

22:58.978 --> 22:59.946
RIGHT OUT OF YOUR MIND,
MISTER.

22:59.979 --> 23:01.013
I SAW HIM FIRST.

23:01.047 --> 23:02.515
BESIDES,
YOU'RE LIVING WITH SOMEONE.

23:02.549 --> 23:04.651
- HE'S LIVING WITH ME.
- WHATEVER.

23:04.684 --> 23:06.886
EITHER WAY,
YOU'RE ALL COMFY AND COZY.

23:06.919 --> 23:08.788
EXCEPT WHEN YOU'RE FUCKING
OTHER GUYS.

23:08.821 --> 23:10.757
- WHO I FUCK
IS NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

23:10.790 --> 23:12.725
OR HIS.

23:15.928 --> 23:16.763
NOW GET OUT.

23:16.796 --> 23:18.197
- WHAT THE FUCK
IS THE MATTER WITH YOU?

23:18.230 --> 23:21.534
- THIS IS IT.

23:21.568 --> 23:25.137
- OH.
[sighs]

23:25.171 --> 23:26.506
THIS IS
A REALLY DUMB IDEA.

23:26.539 --> 23:27.640
COME ON,
LET'S GET OUTTA HERE.

23:27.674 --> 23:29.642
- [laughs] DON'T BE PATHETIC.
YOU MADE A COMMITMENT.

23:29.676 --> 23:30.710
NOW YOU'RE GONNA
GO THROUGH WITH IT.

23:30.743 --> 23:32.144
- YEAH, A LOT YOU KNOW
ABOUT MAKING COMMITMENTS.

23:32.178 --> 23:33.846
- WHICH IS
WHY I NEVER DO.

23:33.880 --> 23:36.048
- [sighs]

23:36.082 --> 23:37.684
- WHAT IF I MAKE A FOOL
OUT OF MYSELF?

23:37.717 --> 23:40.520
- WHO GIVES A SHIT?
